DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260422T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260422T210000
UID:bat-202604221900-mainstage-in-concert-the-ordering-of-mos@bloomingtona
 rts.today
DESCRIPTION:$. Using the Biblical story of Moses\, Dett broadens the terms
  of this individual tale to explore ideas of freedom\, oppression\, and ho
 pe as a cornerstone of American storytelling. This 1937 oratorio is widely
  considered his magnum opus both in compositional scale and in articulatio
 n of identity and artistry.
LOCATION:IU Musical Arts Center
URL:https://operaballet.indiana.edu/events/mainstage-in-concert-dett.html
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
